# Visa Status
# Copy this file to visa_status.md and fill in your own situation.
# This is used by the LLM to assess visa_restriction compatibility and
# to personalise cover letters for eu_only vs. sponsored roles.

- Current visa type: <e.g. EU Blue Card / Chancenkarte / Skilled Worker Visa / EU citizen>
- Work authorization status: <e.g. eligible for immediate start / requires employer sponsorship>
- Availability: <e.g. can start immediately / 3-month notice period>
- Current location: <City, Country>
- Nationality: <Country>
